        <name xml:lang="en">electricity, high voltage</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kWh</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">India has joint hydro projects with Bhutan. Moreover. India imports electricity from Bhutan which are also from the same region. The technology used for electricity generation in that region is assumed as hydro, alpine region.</comment>
